---
title: MCP Orchestration Sequence
description: Sequence diagram showing the flow from User to Orchestrator, Council, and underlying services.
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant Council as Council MCP
    participant Persona as Agent Persona
    participant Cortex as Cortex Memory
    participant Forge as Forge (Tools)
    participant Ollama as Ollama (LLM)

    User->>Orch: Submit Task
    Orch->>Code: Read Config
    Orch->>Cortex: Recall Context
    
    Orch->>Council: Convene Council
    Council->>Persona: Assign Roles (Planner, Critic)
    Persona->>Ollama: Generate Plan
    Ollama-->>Council: Proposed Plan
    
    Council->>Forge: Execute Plan Step
    Forge->>Forge: Run Tool
    Forge-->>Council: Step Result
    
    Council->>Cortex: Store Result
    Council-->>Orch: Task Complete
    Orch-->>User: Final Report
